Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:41.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just as you think he is!\NThat's why you don't have to worry at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish you were Shinichi, Conan...
