Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A friend that! haven't seen in\N5 years called me from my villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that the key\Nwas hidden somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,whenever they wanted to so that his friends could come in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He left it here just for\Nthat very reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because they wouldn't think that\Nthe software that they wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in a place like this would be left so carelessly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And as for the e-mail that\Nthey are about to send here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,look for Mr. Itakura they'll eventually come here to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:44.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the check, and find the software
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without having to see them so he gets to sever all ties with them
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Shinichi... it's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you guys in black!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show your dirty rat selves!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is! The mail!\NOkay, if I open this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Password?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey it's counting down really fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darn
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mail disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darn, It was set so that if it wasn't\Nopened immediately, it would disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, don't tell me that they found out\Nthe mail wasn't opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Not only that, maybe they even\NFound out that the mail failed to be opened
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,using this computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now? They may think that something\Nhappened to Mr. Itakura-and come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.66,0:21:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't come\NTo the phone right now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please record your message after the tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vodka
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They found out. They found out that we\Nfailed to open the e-mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, or maybe they\Nwere watching this villa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aware that they were without Mr. Itakura being
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, if so, how are we going to\NEscape? We're trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're at that villa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:21:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichiu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:22:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and answer me=Mr. Itakura
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.23,0:22:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear me! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.37,0:23:50.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're there at that villa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.08,0:23:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.92,0:24:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we've got no other choice but to\Ncamouflage, ourselves in the blizzard
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.19,0:24:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and make it out the back door
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.12,0:24:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we've still got another way out of this
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.86,0:24:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.16,0:24:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although it can be a bit risky
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.36,0:24:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(3 BFR)
